[ti: 2,478 Kilometers of Wind - English]
[length: 04:14.560]

[00:17.294]I've heard the rain in Jiangnan never stops.
[00:20.942]A sunshine doll hangs by the window.
[00:25.114]Listening in my place to everything you say.
[00:27.971]For the first time, I understood the warmth of being cherished.

[00:32.252]The screen glows faintly in the middle of the night.
[00:35.667]Every word is weighed, written, then hidden away.
[00:39.678]Afraid my initiative might disturb your dreams.
[00:42.594]I set my longing to silent playback.

[00:47.533]A five-year gap, and feelings that never graduated.
[00:51.109]The walls of reality make me choose to step back.
[00:54.718]I dare not get closer, afraid of breaking this peace.
[00:57.891]Quietly waiting for myself to grow up.

[01:02.941]The wind of 2,478 kilometers.
[01:06.955]Becomes five poems and ten nameless songs.
[01:10.536]Enduring every night without a reply.
[01:14.220]A silent crush, yet it still feels comforting.

[01:47.350]Those who don't understand my silence.
[01:50.966]Don't know it's fireworks restrained within.
[01:54.398]Every passage I wrote for you.
[01:58.051]Is my own private refuge.

[02:02.385]A five-year gap, and feelings that never graduated.
[02:06.160]The walls of reality make me choose to step back.
[02:09.739]I dare not get closer, afraid of breaking this peace.
[02:12.933]Quietly waiting for myself to grow up.

[02:16.271]The wind of 2,478 kilometers.
[02:20.316]Becomes five poems and ten nameless songs.
[02:23.801]Enduring every night without a reply.
[02:27.478]A silent crush, yet it still feels comforting.

[02:34.191]Will we meet in Suzhou's spring breeze next year?
[02:37.966]Will traces of you still remain in the future?
[02:41.711]Among so many unknowns, you are the most vivid.
[02:45.695]This insignificant love remains in the wind.

[03:22.506]The wind of 2,478 kilometers.
[03:26.254]Becomes five poems and ten nameless songs.
[03:29.899]Enduring every night without a reply.
[03:33.612]A silent crush, yet it still feels comforting.

[03:42.166]Five poems...
[03:44.277]Ten songs...
[03:47.054]Has the rain in Jiangnan stopped?
[03:52.394]This silent crush...
[03:56.929]I truly like it.